Earth Meld

With the aid of this ritual, a druid may become
one with nature, sinking bodily into the earth and
emerging in the Heart of Geshtai, an ancient druid
sanctum.  From there, it is possible to meld through
the earth to a variety of locations -- those who
master the power have more to choose from.

Command: earthmeld
Base Cost: 65 SP
Base Recovery: long
Base Effect: travel (teleport)
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 21
